    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved green beans</strong>, <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and<strong> sliced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until the onion has softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1656241202423-x200.jpg",
