            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir in your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1656241207594-x200.jpg",
