            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything has softened, add your <strong>udon noodles </strong>to the pan with the <strong>coconut stock </strong>and the<strong> </strong>juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and cook for a further 3 min – these are your <strong>Thai-style coconut udon noodles</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
